The sorting is not stable. If two layers have the same zindex, their order should be kept, so compare `comp_index` in that case:
```suggestion
  size_t ia = (*(ScreenGrid **)a)->comp_index;
  size_t ib = (*(ScreenGrid **)b)->comp_index;
  return za == zb ? (ia == ib ? 0 : (ia < ib ? -1 : 1)) : (za < zb ? -1 : 1);
```

